# Ignore local Claude Code state (settings.local.json, session state, skills,
# any worktrees) but track the committed process docs so the lifecycle travels
# with the checkout. A fully-ignored .claude/ cannot re-include children, so
# ignore the contents and negate the tracked files.
.claude/*
!.claude/dev-workflow.md
!.claude/SETUP.md
graphify-out/
packages/*/types/
.pwf/
